#     + global --verbose/-v + runtime after_help() +
#     `next_line_help(false)` + clap_cargo styles)
#   bin/main.rs lines 108-132 (Subcommands enum: 5 variants
#     including 2 with `visible_alias` and 4 with runtime
#     `after_help = fn()` calls)
#   bin/main.rs lines 134-185 (3 after_help fn-builders:
#     run_after_help, lint_after_help, completions_after_help)
#   src/commands/new/args.rs lines 9-48 (NewArgs:
#     `conflicts_with_all = ["revision", "tag"]` 3-way
#     branch/tag/rev mutex + `last = true, name = "ARGS"`
#     trailing positional)
#   src/commands/build/args.rs lines 21-34 (BuildArgs:
#     optional subcommand + cargo_args flatten + web-
#     feature-gated BuildWebArgs)
#   src/commands/build/args.rs lines 149-174 (BuildWebArgs:
